	<ul>
		<li>Laptop: Macbook Pro 14''
			<ul>
				<li>Chip Apple M1 Pro (2021)</li>
				<li>CPU 8-core</li>
				<li>GPU 14-core</li>
				<li>RAM 16 GB</li>
				<li>512 GB SSD</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Tower PC Win 11:
			<ul>
				<li>AMD Ryzen 7 7800X3D</li>
				<li>Gigabyte WINDFORCE OC GeForce RTX 4070 SUPER 12 GB</li>
				<li>RAM 32 GB</li>
				<li>Samsung 990 Pro M.2-2280 2 TB + 1 TB</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Monitor: BenQ EX351R 35'' Ultra WQHD</li>
		<li>Mouse: Apple Magic Trackpad / Logitech G G305</li>
		<li>Keyboard: Logitech G G713 with <a href="https://www.kiiboom.com/products/kiiboom-x-cosydiaries-rainy-froggy-day-keycap-set">KiiBOOM X Cosydiaries keycap set</a></li>
		<li>Headphones: Sony WH-CH720N</li>
